item.title: Legends of the fall: Women's roller derby champions crash into St. Paul
item.description:
Legends of the fall: Women's roller derby champions crash into St. Paul

The 12 top-ranked women's roller derby teams from across the globe compete this weekend in downtown St. Paul. That includes the local squad, the Minnesota RollerGirls.
